ips4o
------------------------------------------
This is the implementation of the algorithm IPS⁴o presented in the paper
Engineering In-place (Shared-memory) Sorting Algorithms, which contains an
in-depth description of its inner workings, as well as an extensive
experimental performance evaluation.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/ips4o/ips4o

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/ips4o/ips4o.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack ips4o-0+git20250116-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./ips4o-0+git20250116-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ips4o-0+git20250116-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/ips4o-0+git20250116-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

